This paper belongs to the field of wireless communication and network planning, which falls under the category of Network and Communications (cs.NI). The paper discusses the radio propagation models used for LTE, which involves signal processing and transmission, making Information Theory (cs.IT) another likely sub-category. The comparison of different models involves analyzing data and making predictions, which falls under Multimedia (cs.MM) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper also discusses the limitations and drawbacks of the different models, which involves security and privacy concerns, making Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) another possible sub-category.
